message: Zahid 7M is a Writer and Singer. He was born 01 January 2003 in Chittagong.  Bangladesh. a very young age, he started working in music. He is the founder and CEO of Zahid 7M. He has released and worked on more than 10 albums and composed about 100 songs. He also works in the Bangladesh and Indian Music industries. However, he feels comfortable presenting himself as an entrepreneur.
